      <div xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8">
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-Hd1e3741">I, P. 1, Inq. 1, Tract. 6, Q. 6, C. 8</head>
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-Hd1e3744" type="question-title">UTRUM IUSTI POSSINT LAETARI DE PASSIONIBUS, REPROBORUM.</head>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3747">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Item, quaeritur utrum iusti! possint laetari de
          <lb ed="#Q"/>passionibus reproborum.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3754">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Quod non <!--a-->: 1. Psalm. 1: <quote xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-Qd1e3760">Convertantar pecca—
          <lb ed="#Q"/>tores in infernum</quote>. Glossabz: «Non hoc dicit
          <lb ed="#Q"/>optantis adfectu ». .
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3768">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Contra: a. Sancti volunt quod Deus .vult; sed
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Deus vult poenam illorum.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3776">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>b. Item, Apoc. 6,10: Quare non vindicas san<lb ed="#Q"/>guinem
          <lb ed="#Q"/>nostrum? etc
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3785">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>c. Item, Psalm. <!--3-->: Laetabitur iustus,. cum vi<lb ed="#Q"/>derit 
          <lb ed="#Q"/>vindictam..
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3796">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Respondent quidam4 quod aliud est' opw
          <lb ed="#Q"/>tare, aliud velle;" optare enim est concupi<lb ed="#Q"/>scibilis,
          velle rationabilis. Non optant ergo
          <lb ed="#Q"/>poenas malorum, etsi velint,'. quia non de<lb ed="#Q"/>lectantur
          in poenis, etsi ratione m0veantur. —<lb ed="#Q"/>Contra5:
          Laetabitar iustus, tam viderit vinn
          <lb ed="#Q"/>dictam etc.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c8-d1e3814">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Respondeo: Poena reproborum, secundum
          <lb ed="#Q"/>quod refertur ad naturam patientem, non de<lb ed="#Q"/>lectat
          sanctos; sed secundum quod'refertur' ad
          <lb ed="#Q"/>divinam iustitiam poenam inferentem, sic de»
          <lb ed="#Q"/>lectat eos.
        </p>
      </div>
